---
title: Ras-el-hanout Spiced Pork with couscous, yoghurt and cranberry chutney
description: Peas, peppers and pork come together along with ras-el-hanout spice blend and cranberry chutney to create a recipe that's anything but ordinary. Try something different for dinner this week!
